SubjectAddition to Campbell River Indian Reserve No. 11, British Columbia
PrecisOrder setting apart 14.276 hectares (35.276 acres) of land, for the use and benefit of the CAMPBELL RIVER INDIAN BAND as an addition to CAMPBELL RIVER INDIAN RESERVE NO. 11, in the City of Campbell River, on its northeastern edge, British Columbia.
